data.title: Sean Doherty: Credits, Bio, News & More
data.meta_description: Searching to find out more about Sean Doherty? We have a full Biography, Photos, Theatre Credits, TV and Movies, Videos and more! Check out Sean Doherty's bio now including film and tv, as well as on stage.
data.text:
Sean Doherty News

Performers Set for NEO 2024: A CONCERT CELEBRATION at The Green Room 42

The York Theatre Company has revealed the artists scheduled to perform at the celebrated concert series NEO. See who is performing and learn how to purchase tickets.

Mark MacKillop to Present Fourth Edition of DUETS at Chelsea Table + Stage

CHELSEA TABLE + STAGE will present the return of Mark MacKillop, star of West Side Story, Anastasia and Dirty Dancing, with the fourth installment of his “Duets” series. Learn how to purchase tickets.

Review: JAGGED LITTLE PILL at Lied Center For The Performing Arts

What did our critic think of JAGGED LITTLE PILL at Lied Center For The Performing Arts?

JAGGED LITTLE PILL Comes to The Bushnell in May

The Bushnell announced that tickets for the Hartford premiere of Jagged Little Pill, running May 9-14, are on sale now.

Alanis Morissette's JAGGED LITTLE PILL Comes to the Benedum Center This Month

The Pittsburgh Cultural Trust has announced the PNC Broadway in Pittsburgh 2022-2023 season will present the area premier of Alanis Morissette's JAGGED LITTLE PILL, at the Benedum Center from January 24 to 29, 2023.

Tickets To Go On Sale This Week for JAGGED LITTLE PILL at The Providence Performing Arts Center

Individual tickets for the Providence premiere of JAGGED LITTLE PILL at The Providence Performing Arts Center will go on sale on Wednesday, December 14, 2022 at 10A.

Single Tickets to JAGGED LITTLE PILL at Proctors Go On Sale Wednesday

Proctors announced that individual tickets for the Schenectady premiere of JAGGED LITTLE PILL will go on sale Wednesday, Nov. 23 at 10 a.m.

Tickets On Sale For JAGGED LITTLE PILL At Kalamazoo's Miller Auditorium

MILLER AUDITORIUM has announced that individual tickets for the West Michigan premiere of JAGGED LITTLE PILL will go on sale November 16th, 2022, at 10:00 A.M.

JAGGED LITTLE PILL Comes To The Fisher Theatre, February 14 - 26, 2023

Broadway In Detroit announced today that individual tickets for the Detroit premiere of JAGGED LITTLE PILL will go on sale Friday, November 18 at 10:00 a.m.

JAGGED LITTLE PILL Announced At Aronoff Center

Individual tickets for the Cincinnati premiere of JAGGED LITTLE PILL are now on sale at Aronoff Center.

Video: Cydney Kutcipal & Lauren Chanel Sing 'Hand in My Pocket' From JAGGED LITTLE PILL

The National Tour of Jagged Little Pill, making its way around the country, is currently playing at the Golden Gate Theatre in San Francisco through November 6, 2022. See Cydney Kutcipal & Lauren Chanel sing 'Hand in My Pocket' from the dressing room of the Golden Gate Theatre here!

JAGGED LITTLE PILL Comes To Keller Auditorium in November

Broadway in Portland has announced the Portland premiere of JAGGED LITTLE PILL, playing Keller Auditorium from November 15 - 20. Inspired by the seminal rock album of the same name by seven-time Grammy Award winner Alanis Morissette (she/her), tickets to the Tony and Grammy Award-winning production are available now are available now.

JAGGED LITTLE PILL Comes To The Paramount Theatre Next Month

The Seattle premiere of JAGGED LITTLE PILL is playing The Paramount Theatre from November 8 – 13. Inspired by the seminal rock album of the same name by seven-time Grammy Award winner Alanis Morissette (she/her), tickets to the Tony and Grammy award-winning production are available now on-line.

Photos: First Look at Heidi Blickenstaff, Jade McLeod, Dillon Klena & More in JAGGED LITTLE PILL National Tour

The National Tour of Jagged Little Pill is making its way across the country. Heidi Blickenstaff is reprising her role from the Broadway production as Mary Jane Healy, and is joined by Lauren Chanel as Frankie Healy, Chris Hoch as Steve Healy and Dillon Klena as Nick Healy. Get a first look at photos here!

JAGGED LITTLE PILL is Now on Sale at DPAC

Inspired by the seminal rock album of the same name by seven-time Grammy Award winner Alanis Morissette (she/her), JAGGED LITTLE PILL will premiere at DPAC February 28 – March 5, as part of Truist Broadway at DPAC.

Review Roundup: JAGGED LITTLE PILL on Tour; Read All of the Reviews!

The National Tour of Jagged Little Pill is now underway! The tour opened in Las Vegas on September 6. Read all of the reviews for Jagged Little Pill on tour.

Tickets For JAGGED LITTLE PILL in Baltimore on Sale Today

The Hippodrome Theatre at the France-Merrick Performing Arts Center announced that individual tickets for the Baltimore premiere of JAGGED LITTLE PILL go on sale Friday, September 16 at 10 a.m. EST.

Dillon Klena, Lauren Chanel, Jade McLeod, Chris Hoch & More Join JAGGED LITTLE PILL Tour; Full Cast Announced

Full casting has been announced for the national tour of Jagged Little Pill which will have its premiere September 6th in Las Vegas at Reynolds Hall. The full cast includes Heidi Blickenstaff (Mary Jane Healy), Lauren Chanel (Frankie), Chris Hoch (Steve), Dillon Klena (Nick), Jade Mcleod (Jo), Allison Sheppard (Bella), Rishi Golani (Phoenix), and more.

Diversionary Announces The Cast and Creative Team of the World Premiere Musical EIGHTY-SIXED

Diversionary announces the cast and creative team of the World Premiere Musical of EIGHTY-SIXED. Kevin Newbury will direct the World Premiere production of EIGHTY-SIXED by Jeremy J. King and Sam Salmond and choreographed by Raja Feather Kelly.
